OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTaliban bans women from    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FAfghan universities        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Taliban have announced the closure 
OL,6, of universities to women in            
OL,7, Afghanistan, according to a letter by  
OL,8, the higher education minister.         
OL,10,FThe minister says the move is until    
OL,11,Ffurther notice. It is expected to take 
OL,12,Feffect immediately.                    
OL,14,FIt further restricts women's access to 
OL,15,Fformal education, as they were already 
OL,16,Fexcluded from most secondary schools.  
OL,18,FOne Kabul University student told the  
OL,19,FBBC she had been crying since she heard
OL,20,Fthe news.                              
